text: The Nokia E72 is a smartphone from the Nokia Eseries, developed by Nokia as the successor to the Nokia E71. It was announced on June 15, 2009 at the Nokia Connections event in Singapore. It was discontinued on March 7, 2011. == Related pages == * Nokia Eseries * Nokia E5-00 (Reduced cost version of the E72) * Nokia E71 * Nokia E73 Mode == References == == Further reading == * * == Other websites == * Nokia E72 Full Phone Specification *Device details -- Nokia E72 Category:Nokia mobile phones
